having read the reviews for johnnys we looked forward to eating there during our stay in new york, and we werent dissapointed!.....eggs and bacon with home fries! so tasty and delicous.....plus pancakes bacon and maple syrup plates soon empty.the diner has a great buz about it...staff welcoming n friendly, even tho rushed off there feet,.........we ate there twice during our week stay and look forward to our next visit next time we are in nyc. 5star dinner. kev and gail,west midlands,england
